# DevFlow Automator - Kiro Hero Week 2 Challenge

## Project Overview
**"I hate doing repetitive dev tasks, so I built this Swiss Army knife"**

DevFlow Automator is a comprehensive CLI tool that tackles multiple developer pain points in one unified solution. Instead of building separate tools for each task, this project combines the most annoying developer workflows into a single, AI-powered automation suite.

## The Problem
As developers, we spend countless hours on repetitive tasks:
- Writing the same commit messages over and over
- Manually updating README badges when they break
- Setting up identical project structures
- Tracking coding time across projects
- Keeping documentation in sync with code changes
- Writing boilerplate code for common patterns

